contentrichtext.text: '''John Moores''' may refer to: *[[John H. Moores]] (1821–1880), American businessman and politician in the state of Oregon *Sir [[John Moores (British businessman)]] (1896–1993), British businessman who founded Littlewoods *[[John Moores (baseball)]] (born 1944), American entrepreneur and former owner of the San Diego Padres *[[Liverpool John Moores University]], a university in Liverpool, England, named after Sir John Moores ==See also== *[[John Moore (disambiguation)]] {{hndis|Moores, John}}
